textBox.richText: This generation includes, and is limited to: Pokémon Black and White. As they are DS games, much like the last generation, the process is actually similar. The more specific tools however, will be mostly different. Fifth Generation Hacking tools: http://tinyurl.com/5vgtools Download a specific tool or view unarchived package: http://tinyurl.com/5vgview These games are not out in America yet, as denoted by the date above. Hacking progress will improve once they are officially released in English.
